            "description": "This international project examines the nature and extent of the changes experienced by the academic profession in recent years. it explores both the reasons for and the consequences of these changes. It considers the implications of the changes for the attractiveness of the academic profession as a career and for the ability of the academic community to contribute to the further development of knowledge societies and the attainment of national goals. It makes comparisons on these matters between twenty national higher education systems across Europe, Asia, North and South America. ",
